    "It also acts as a highly advanced auto-complete in an IDE, offering code optimizations and suggestions.",
    "CoPilot focuses mainly on code completion, while ChatGPT prioritizes providing ideas, explanations, and then generating code.",
    "With ChatGPT, developers can describe what they want the code to do in plain English and have the code generated for them.",
    "To compare ChatGPT and CoPilot, please see here.Although ChatGPT is a proficient coder, it falls short in terms of being a top-notch software engineer or developer.",
